title: Artist Spotlight: Tyler Hobbs and Proof Collective's Grail #19, Wall
description: Tyler Hobbs, the NFT artist of Art Blocks fame, walks Ryan Carson, Proof's COO, through his process in creating the photorealistic image of "Wall" in Grails by Proof Collective, revealed to be entirely generative.
